Phil The Comic Guy is using a Reading  
Order List that I created. His Chapter Titles are exactly the same as
mine,  
and the website page I created had been started in April 2012.

If you go to my webpage, you'll see I have the same list, with my dates
and  
updates, summaries, a release schedule, and additional content.

Phil The Comic Guy is taking a portion of my content and calling it his
own.
